[1] WHO: Ebola virus death toll reaches 7693
Date: 26 Dec 2014
Source: Tass [edited]
http://itar-tass.com/en/world/769562


As many as 19 695 are infected, the World Health Organization (WHO) said on Fri [26 Dec 2014]. These cases were reported from Guinea, Liberia, and Sierra Leone.

The most serious situation is reported from Liberia, with 3384 deaths. Sierra Leone has the largest number of infected, 9203. In Guinea, 1654 deaths and 2630 cases are registered. The number of Ebola deaths in these 3 countries rose by 120 since 24 Dec 2014...

[ref: WHO sitrep http://apps.who.int/gho/data/view.ebola-sitrep.ebola-summary-latest?lang=en. - Mod.JW]

