[6] Sierra Leone: nurses stay off work due to non-payment of hazard pay
Date: 25 Dec 2014
Source: IB Times (Reuters) [edited]
http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/ebola-nurses-stay-off-work-due-non-payment-hazard-pay-1480969


A hazard payment delay has led to nurses striking work in Sierra Leone. Nurses at a public hospital in Makeni in northern Sierra Leone went on strike on Thu [25 Dec 2014], claiming that hazard pay for the month of November [2014] had not been paid by the government. Around 30 nurses at the Mabenteh Hospital stayed off work...

[byline: Jayalakshmi K]

